        "title": "Introduction",
        "displayTitle": "",
        "body": "<b>Spark Post lets people create professional graphics in seconds.</b> <br><br><br> While it leverages concepts from Adobe’s pro tools like Photoshop and InDesign, like the ability to layer images with text and filters, it makes this accessible to everyday users who can make these sorts of changes just by tapping buttons.<br><br><br> Get started with our suggested professionally-designed template and make it your own with a few simple steps and turn your text and photo into a professional-looking graphic by simply applying your favorite theme. With Spark Post you don't need design experience to create beautiful images.",
